# Project AEGIS - Cyber Defense Dashboard

## Overview
This project analyzes server log data to detect suspicious activities based on HTTP status codes.

## Features
- Detects suspicious requests (status code >= 400)
- Calculates attack percentage
- Displays results on a simple dashboard

## Tech Stack
- Python (Flask)
- Pandas
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript

## How to Run

1. Install dependencies:
pip install flask pandas

2. Run backend:
python app.py

3. Open frontend:
index.html (use Live Server)

## API Endpoint
http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/data

